This is the "Barcode" iOS application that had been available on the iOS App Store since its launch.

The application version of Stefan has not been updated for a while and is still linked against iOS 2.1.

This fork links against iOS 6 and zxing compilation problems are fixed, 
XCODE 3.2 is required to open the projects

Additionally the ZDBar Library is used to support scanning of UPC barcodes.
